      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014an affordable entry point for someone who sees potential instead of perfection. It\u2019s the sort of machine that feels like the start of a story: a budget-friendly daily, a hands-on project, or a practical backup with plenty of life left for the right owner. If you appreciate grit, value, and the chance to make something your own, this one is worth a look.",
